						               													<description>It is easy to get lost on sea without a map. Help Rumini to put the map's torn pieces together so that he can find his magical tools!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;It is all done as a tile laying game where each tile is a piece of the map the players build. Each piece has a small icon in the corner indicating magic tools that can be collected which is also the goal of the game. Laying a tile is done through playing cards from a hand of four which does not change throughout the game as players redraw from a main deck to replace the one they played.&amp;#10;There are also some special cards that can help or challenge the players. These are just put aside and can be used at will.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;All in all Rumini - The Torn Map is an exciting, quick game where beside luck you will also need some tactical skills and good memory.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;T&amp;eacute;rk&amp;eacute;p n&amp;eacute;lk&amp;uuml;l hamar elvesz&amp;uuml;nk a tengeren. Seg&amp;iacute;ts Rumininak &amp;ouml;sszeilleszteni a sz&amp;eacute;tszakadt t&amp;eacute;rk&amp;eacute;p darabjait, hogy miel&amp;#197;&amp;#145;bb meg tal&amp;aacute;lhassa a var&amp;aacute;zseszk&amp;ouml;z&amp;ouml;ket!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Izgalmas, p&amp;ouml;rg&amp;#197;&amp;#145;s k&amp;aacute;rtyaj&amp;aacute;t&amp;eacute;k, melyben a szerencse mellett sokkal ink&amp;aacute;bb a taktik&amp;aacute;z&amp;aacute;s, &amp;eacute;s a j&amp;oacute; megfigyel&amp;#197;&amp;#145;k&amp;eacute;szs&amp;eacute;g kap szerepet.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
